# ─── Dispatcharr VPN egress (Gluetun → ExpressVPN, custom OpenVPN) ────────────
# Dispatcharr's outbound IPTV traffic egresses through this tunnel so the apps
# VM's residential IP isn't exposed to the provider. See the compose file header
# for the full rationale. Injected into the Gluetun container via env_file.
#
# These are NOT your normal ExpressVPN login. Get them from:
#   expressvpn.com → Advanced Setup → Manual Configuration → OpenVPN
# That page shows a dedicated OpenVPN username + password — paste them here, and
# download a server .ovpn from the same page to services/dispatcharr/expressvpn.ovpn
# (that file picks the egress location; it carries the CA + tls-crypt key Gluetun's
# built-in ExpressVPN profile is missing).
OPENVPN_USER=
OPENVPN_PASSWORD=
